1
00:00:00,634 --> 00:00:03,872
<i>♫ The dusk awakens ♫</i>

2
00:00:04,768 --> 00:00:08,352
<i>♫ The slumber of the whales ♫</i>

3
00:00:11,872 --> 00:00:15,200
<i>♫ Swimming towards the galaxy ♫</i>

4
00:00:16,128 --> 00:00:20,992
<i>♫ It docks at the blue shore of my heart ♫</i>

5
00:00:20,992 --> 00:00:25,984
<i>♫ I hear the poems coming from afar ♫</i>

6
00:00:26,624 --> 00:00:32,224
<i>♫ Happiness and sorrow come and go ♫</i>

7
00:00:32,224 --> 00:00:37,792
<i>♫ As my memories dance along the clouds ♫</i>

8
00:00:37,792 --> 00:00:41,600
<i>♫ I still remember ♫</i>

9
00:00:43,424 --> 00:00:49,216
<i>♫ Please wait for me at the horizon ♫</i>

10
00:00:49,216 --> 00:00:52,480
<i>♫ We'll watch the sunset together ♫</i>

11
00:00:54,720 --> 00:01:00,352
<i>♫ Whose dream hasn't been beautiful ♫</i>

12
00:01:00,352 --> 00:01:04,512
<i>♫ When have I ever been myself ♫</i>

13
00:01:06,080 --> 00:01:11,840
<i>♫ Wait for me at the end of the daydream ♫</i>

14
00:01:11,840 --> 00:01:15,264
<i>♫ Who has wandered within it ♫</i>

15
00:01:17,344 --> 00:01:22,304
<i>♫ Life is nothing more than fantasy ♫</i>

16
00:01:23,168 --> 00:01:25,498
<i>♫ I am still me ♫</i>

17
00:01:25,498 --> 00:01:29,722
<i>[You Are Desire]</i>

18
00:01:29,722 --> 00:01:33,754
<i>[Episode 5: Will You Cheer for Me]</i>

19
00:01:34,304 --> 00:01:35,488
Where's your application form?

20
00:01:36,603 --> 00:01:37,722
What application form?

21
00:01:39,963 --> 00:01:41,423
You have to fill in this application form

22
00:01:41,423 --> 00:01:43,123
and ask your parent to sign it.

23
00:01:46,603 --> 00:01:47,682
My parent?

24
00:01:47,682 --> 00:01:49,742
Without parental consent,
you're not allowed to live in the dormitory.

25
00:01:49,742 --> 00:01:51,123
Don't you know about it?

26
00:01:54,002 --> 00:01:55,104
Okay.

27
00:02:35,243 --> 00:02:36,704
This case is very important.

28
00:02:36,704 --> 00:02:38,848
But now, the existing evidence is
quite unfavorable to us.

29
00:02:39,562 --> 00:02:42,170
I plan to talk to
the parties involved tomorrow.

30
00:02:42,170 --> 00:02:43,770
Help me prepare more materials.

31
00:02:54,720 --> 00:02:55,808
What's wrong?

32
00:03:05,344 --> 00:03:06,528
Hey, brother.

33
00:03:07,866 --> 00:03:09,086
Just spill it.

34
00:03:09,086 --> 00:03:11,968
Care to spare me a few minutes?

35
00:03:13,664 --> 00:03:14,720
You'll have two minutes.

36
00:03:15,274 --> 00:03:16,994
- You!
- One minute left.

37
00:03:18,522 --> 00:03:20,096
Okay, I'll make it quick.

38
00:03:20,096 --> 00:03:21,248
I want to live on campus,

39
00:03:21,248 --> 00:03:22,304
but I need parental consent.

40
00:03:22,304 --> 00:03:23,362
Can you sign my form? Thanks.

41
00:03:25,842 --> 00:03:26,962
Why don't you ask your dad?

42
00:03:26,962 --> 00:03:28,661
He's not at home.

43
00:03:28,661 --> 00:03:29,982
You can have your dad sign it

44
00:03:29,982 --> 00:03:31,041
and upload a scanned copy.

45
00:03:33,281 --> 00:03:34,282
If I could do that,

46
00:03:34,282 --> 00:03:35,661
I would have done it a long time ago.

47
00:03:35,661 --> 00:03:37,682
Brother, can you sign it?

48
00:03:38,432 --> 00:03:39,488
No.

49
00:03:41,842 --> 00:03:43,962
Don't you want me to move out?

50
00:03:43,962 --> 00:03:46,242
Just sign it, and I'll leave immediately.

51
00:03:48,160 --> 00:03:49,601
That's a different matter.

52
00:03:53,281 --> 00:03:54,521
Your dad is your guardian,

53
00:03:54,521 --> 00:03:56,001
so only he can sign this form.

54
00:03:56,802 --> 00:03:57,902
I don't have the right.

55
00:03:57,902 --> 00:03:59,402
So,

56
00:03:59,402 --> 00:04:00,962
you're not going to help me. Right?

57
00:04:02,161 --> 00:04:03,482
I don't have the right to help you.

58
00:04:03,482 --> 00:04:05,856
Okay then, I won't bother you.

59
00:04:19,322 --> 00:04:21,402
<i>If you won't apply for that scholarship,</i>

60
00:04:21,402 --> 00:04:22,422
<i>can you let me have it?</i>

61
00:04:22,422 --> 00:04:23,701
<i>How do you know I'm not applying?</i>

62
00:04:23,701 --> 00:04:25,202
<i>It's such a good opportunity.</i>

63
00:04:25,202 --> 00:04:26,442
<i>I certainly can't waste it.</i>

64
00:04:26,442 --> 00:04:28,762
<i>Isn't there only one scholarship slot?</i>

65
00:04:28,762 --> 00:04:29,962
<i>How would I have it?</i>

66
00:04:30,481 --> 00:04:32,262
<i>Shen Juan gave up his spot,</i>

67
00:04:32,262 --> 00:04:34,041
<i>so it's yours now.</i>

68
00:04:48,801 --> 00:04:51,282
Shen Juan, I received the scholarship.

69
00:04:51,282 --> 00:04:52,544
Thank you.

70
00:04:52,544 --> 00:04:54,801
You're welcome, Lin Cuihua.

71
00:04:55,642 --> 00:04:56,882
You can use your scholarship

72
00:04:56,882 --> 00:05:00,361
to make your village look fancier.

73
00:05:04,402 --> 00:05:05,801
So, about the monthly exam,

74
00:05:07,041 --> 00:05:08,742
can we consider it settled?

75
00:05:08,742 --> 00:05:10,082
Class, it's time for the lesson.

76
00:05:11,281 --> 00:05:13,202
Please take out your monthly exam papers.

77
00:05:15,161 --> 00:05:17,582
All of you did well in this month's exam,

78
00:05:17,582 --> 00:05:19,402
especially Lin Yujing.

79
00:05:20,281 --> 00:05:22,682
I've already checked everyone's paper.

80
00:05:22,682 --> 00:05:25,382
Most mistakes are from the cloze test.

81
00:05:25,382 --> 00:05:26,582
For example,

82
00:05:29,921 --> 00:05:31,142
this question has four options.

83
00:05:31,142 --> 00:05:33,002
Everyone gets confused easily.

84
00:05:34,121 --> 00:05:35,842
When dealing with this kind of questions,

85
00:05:35,842 --> 00:05:37,241
there's a specific technique.

86
00:05:38,481 --> 00:05:41,361
Firstly, make sure
to read the context carefully

87
00:05:41,361 --> 00:05:42,882
and understand the main idea of the article.

88
00:05:43,681 --> 00:05:45,161
This is the basis for
answering these questions.

89
00:05:46,041 --> 00:05:47,601
When you do your exercises,

90
00:05:48,241 --> 00:05:49,541
if you can't understand
the meaning of an article,

91
00:05:49,541 --> 00:05:50,962
read it several times more.

92
00:05:52,082 --> 00:05:54,481
Your abilities will improve

93
00:05:55,281 --> 00:05:57,442
only if you can answer the questions
after understanding the article.

94
00:05:58,688 --> 00:05:59,776
Secondly,

95
00:06:00,322 --> 00:06:02,681
you should learn more phrases and sentences

96
00:06:03,241 --> 00:06:05,082
and master their collocation.

97
00:06:05,842 --> 00:06:07,241
As you learn more, you'll make fewer mistakes.

98
00:06:08,202 --> 00:06:09,721
Here's a method.

99
00:06:10,656 --> 00:06:11,776
During the exam,

100
00:06:11,776 --> 00:06:14,681
if you really can't decide
which option to choose,

101
00:06:15,562 --> 00:06:18,464
combine the optional choices into the article

102
00:06:19,041 --> 00:06:20,921
and read the context again.

103
00:06:21,882 --> 00:06:24,842
This can help you choose the correct option.

104
00:06:54,481 --> 00:06:55,712
Shen Juan.

105
00:06:58,402 --> 00:06:59,681
My dear deskmate.

106
00:07:02,368 --> 00:07:03,584
Don't be creepy.

107
00:07:04,762 --> 00:07:05,942
Help me out, will you?

108
00:07:05,942 --> 00:07:07,840
Can you help me sign this form?

109
00:07:11,322 --> 00:07:13,792
Lin Cuihua, you are asking for a favor again.

110
00:07:14,762 --> 00:07:15,942
Alas, I was born poor.

111
00:07:15,942 --> 00:07:17,920
My heartless dad doesn't care about me.

112
00:07:18,481 --> 00:07:19,922
So, if you sign for me,

113
00:07:19,922 --> 00:07:21,152
we'll call it even.

114
00:07:23,082 --> 00:07:24,882
Whose name should I sign? Mine?

115
00:07:24,882 --> 00:07:26,181
My dad's, of course.

116
00:07:26,181 --> 00:07:28,041
So you want me to be your dad?

117
00:07:29,281 --> 00:07:31,301
Shen Juan, I'm serious!

118
00:07:31,301 --> 00:07:33,161
Lin Yujing, someone's looking for you.

119
00:08:18,522 --> 00:08:19,541
<i>[Big news!]</i>

120
00:08:19,541 --> 00:08:21,962
<i>[We will have an inter-school sports meet
with Puhua next week!]</i>

121
00:08:23,082 --> 00:08:25,702
<i>[Puhua is the best high school in Pucheng.]</i>

122
00:08:25,702 --> 00:08:27,462
<i>[All the talented students in Pucheng]</i>

123
00:08:27,462 --> 00:08:29,042
<i>[are studying in Puhua High School.]</i>

124
00:08:29,042 --> 00:08:31,182
<i>[What's the point of
competing with them on a sports meet?]</i>

125
00:08:31,182 --> 00:08:32,602
<i>[Don't be so pathetic.]</i>

126
00:08:32,602 --> 00:08:34,262
<i>[We have advantages too!]</i>

127
00:08:34,262 --> 00:08:35,842
<i>[I'll find out
what Puhua students are talking about.]</i>

128
00:08:37,641 --> 00:08:39,282
<i>[We'll definitely
win the track and field events this year.]</i>

129
00:08:39,282 --> 00:08:40,801
<i>[Lu Yao can make sure of it.]</i>

130
00:08:40,801 --> 00:08:42,501
<i>[What I'm concerned about now is]</i>

131
00:08:42,501 --> 00:08:44,802
<i>[can Lu Yao break our school record?]</i>

132
00:08:45,601 --> 00:08:46,742
<i>[Of course!]</i>

133
00:08:46,742 --> 00:08:48,561
<i>[Our track and field team is very strong,]</i>

134
00:08:48,561 --> 00:08:50,641
<i>[but since it's an away game,
the conditions might be a bit tough.]</i>

135
00:09:05,962 --> 00:09:07,121
<i>This is my friend, Lu Yao.</i>

136
00:09:08,282 --> 00:09:09,442
<i>This is my deskmate, Shen Juan.</i>

137
00:09:17,042 --> 00:09:18,080
Still awake?

138
00:09:18,601 --> 00:09:19,601
I'm going to sleep now.

139
00:09:21,001 --> 00:09:22,321
Don't push yourself too hard.

140
00:09:22,321 --> 00:09:24,562
Rest early.
Don't you have to wake up early tomorrow?

141
00:09:25,562 --> 00:09:27,382
Okay, I will. Rest well.

142
00:09:27,382 --> 00:09:28,448
Lock the door.

143
00:09:28,448 --> 00:09:29,521
Okay.

144
00:09:44,641 --> 00:09:45,682
Everyone, quiet down.

145
00:09:46,202 --> 00:09:47,542
I have an announcement.

146
00:09:47,542 --> 00:09:50,602
You all know about
the sports meet with Puhua, right?

147
00:09:50,602 --> 00:09:53,802
I would like to pick some students
who are good at sports.

148
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:56,000
Any volunteers?

149
00:09:57,202 --> 00:09:58,661
I'll do long jump.

150
00:09:58,661 --> 00:10:00,288
Then I'll sign up for high jump.

151
00:10:04,992 --> 00:10:06,080
Anyone else?

152
00:10:09,401 --> 00:10:11,822
This is our last sports meet in high school.

153
00:10:11,822 --> 00:10:13,442
I hope everyone can be more enthusiastic.

154
00:10:13,442 --> 00:10:15,222
There are still many slots for
track and field events.

155
00:10:15,222 --> 00:10:16,641
Any volunteers?

156
00:10:18,082 --> 00:10:19,102
I heard that

157
00:10:19,102 --> 00:10:22,202
the athletes from Puhua High School
are all their best ones.

158
00:10:22,202 --> 00:10:23,462
Especially their ace,

159
00:10:23,462 --> 00:10:24,522
Lu Yao.

160
00:10:24,522 --> 00:10:26,282
He's participating in
several track and field events.

161
00:10:26,282 --> 00:10:27,722
If he joins the game, I'll give up.

162
00:10:27,722 --> 00:10:28,802
I won't embarrass myself.

163
00:10:29,842 --> 00:10:30,922
I mean, that's Lu Yao!

164
00:10:30,922 --> 00:10:32,482
Nobody would want to challenge him.

165
00:10:32,482 --> 00:10:34,242
He's a star at Puhua High School.

166
00:10:34,242 --> 00:10:36,522
They said he's a handsome guy with good grades.

167
00:10:36,522 --> 00:10:37,761
He's basically good at everything!

168
00:10:39,721 --> 00:10:42,442
It's okay. You can come to sign up
when you've made up your mind.

169
00:10:48,320 --> 00:10:49,322
Juan,

170
00:10:49,881 --> 00:10:52,022
this is a once-in-a-century duel!

171
00:10:52,022 --> 00:10:53,362
Are you interested?

172
00:10:53,362 --> 00:10:54,941
What's so good about Lu Yao?

173
00:10:54,941 --> 00:10:57,202
We have Shen Juan!

174
00:10:57,202 --> 00:10:59,562
Juan, time to teach them a lesson.

175
00:11:00,448 --> 00:11:01,504
I'm not interested.

176
00:11:02,912 --> 00:11:06,302
When has Juan ever gone to sports field

177
00:11:06,302 --> 00:11:07,922
except when playing basketball
and doing group exercises?

178
00:11:07,922 --> 00:11:10,401
Well, there's no table on the sports field
to let him sleep on.

179
00:11:11,401 --> 00:11:12,702
Are you going to sign up, then?

180
00:11:12,702 --> 00:11:14,142
Go ahead! Come on!

181
00:11:14,142 --> 00:11:15,168
Me?

182
00:11:17,641 --> 00:11:18,761
If Shen Juan signs up, I'll follow him.

183
00:11:34,322 --> 00:11:35,601
Why are you here again?

184
00:11:37,601 --> 00:11:39,322
I'm here to check on your sports field.

185
00:11:40,322 --> 00:11:42,400
Can't you even come up with a new excuse?
You said that last time.

186
00:11:43,881 --> 00:11:45,001
What is it?

187
00:11:45,001 --> 00:11:47,581
Our school is recruiting for
a minority language specialty class.

188
00:11:47,581 --> 00:11:49,562
With your French level,
you can definitely get in.

189
00:11:52,521 --> 00:11:53,681
Our Puhua High School,

190
00:11:53,681 --> 00:11:55,421
is the ace of private schools.

191
00:11:55,421 --> 00:11:56,422
What do you mean?

192
00:11:56,422 --> 00:11:58,080
Do you want me to transfer there?

193
00:11:59,904 --> 00:12:01,042
I already asked them.

194
00:12:01,042 --> 00:12:03,741
This specialty class has a preferential policy.

195
00:12:03,741 --> 00:12:05,801
Not only can you get free accommodation,

196
00:12:05,801 --> 00:12:08,622
but you can also
get a high amount of scholarships

197
00:12:08,622 --> 00:12:10,202
if you can become the top three of your class.

198
00:12:10,202 --> 00:12:11,322
See? If you join this class,

199
00:12:11,322 --> 00:12:13,301
you won't need to worry about
money and accommodation, right?

200
00:12:13,301 --> 00:12:15,232
You'll be out of your dad's control.

201
00:12:17,024 --> 00:12:18,048
Here. Take it.

202
00:12:23,842 --> 00:12:24,902
Who is this boy?

203
00:12:24,902 --> 00:12:26,622
Why isn't he wearing our school uniform?

204
00:12:26,622 --> 00:12:27,902
He's quite handsome, though.

205
00:12:27,902 --> 00:12:29,202
Is he from our school?

206
00:12:29,202 --> 00:12:30,382
How come I've never seen him before?

207
00:12:30,382 --> 00:12:31,424
Do me a favor, will you?

208
00:12:32,042 --> 00:12:34,282
I need a set of uniform.

209
00:12:34,816 --> 00:12:35,842
What do you want to do?

210
00:12:36,601 --> 00:12:37,942
I want to keep a low profile.

211
00:12:37,942 --> 00:12:39,802
You don't want everyone to notice me, right?

212
00:12:40,922 --> 00:12:42,842
Okay, wait here.

213
00:13:12,562 --> 00:13:14,002
That guy is so handsome!

214
00:13:14,002 --> 00:13:15,322
Although you're wearing our school uniform,

215
00:13:15,322 --> 00:13:16,562
you're still quite noticeable.

216
00:13:26,881 --> 00:13:27,982
So why did you want our uniform?

217
00:13:27,982 --> 00:13:30,222
You're not trying to sneak in
and scout us, are you?

218
00:13:30,222 --> 00:13:31,962
I won't collude with the enemy.

219
00:13:32,601 --> 00:13:35,162
Anyway, we'll soon become schoolmates.

220
00:13:35,162 --> 00:13:36,384
I'm not your enemy.

221
00:13:36,960 --> 00:13:38,562
No way. I won't be your schoolmate.

222
00:13:47,481 --> 00:13:48,576
Where's my uniform?

223
00:13:59,802 --> 00:14:01,922
Puhua Admissions Brochure?

224
00:14:02,842 --> 00:14:03,922
Why does Lin Yujing have this?

225
00:14:13,888 --> 00:14:15,042
Hold on.

226
00:14:15,042 --> 00:14:16,721
Lin Yujing has just transferred here,
and she's already leaving?

227
00:14:17,856 --> 00:14:18,922
Hey, let me tell you.

228
00:14:18,922 --> 00:14:20,582
Someone is running around the sports field
as fast as lightning.

229
00:14:20,582 --> 00:14:21,722
Looks like he's trained.

230
00:14:21,722 --> 00:14:23,362
I think he's a freshman.

231
00:14:23,362 --> 00:14:24,822
What freshman?

232
00:14:24,822 --> 00:14:26,162
Seems like he's from Puhua.

233
00:14:26,721 --> 00:14:28,002
Let's go! Let's go check it out.

234
00:14:28,002 --> 00:14:29,322
Come on! Hurry!

235
00:14:29,881 --> 00:14:30,962
- Let's follow them.
- Wait for me!

236
00:14:30,962 --> 00:14:32,064
Let's go!

237
00:14:39,552 --> 00:14:40,672
Thanks.

238
00:14:41,322 --> 00:14:43,102
You really are here to scout us.

239
00:14:43,102 --> 00:14:45,402
You even showed off in our uniform!

240
00:14:45,402 --> 00:14:46,601
We can't be friends anymore.

241
00:14:47,802 --> 00:14:49,922
Come on. I need to learn about my enemy
before securing the victory.

242
00:14:49,922 --> 00:14:51,522
You saw the game just now.

243
00:14:51,522 --> 00:14:54,560
Your school is far behind mine.

244
00:14:54,560 --> 00:14:55,584
See?

245
00:14:55,584 --> 00:14:56,922
You're wasting your time here.

246
00:14:56,922 --> 00:14:58,842
Well, I'll make this decision for you.

247
00:14:58,842 --> 00:15:00,562
You'll transfer to
Puhua High School right away.

248
00:15:01,216 --> 00:15:02,241
Huh, that's funny.

249
00:15:10,528 --> 00:15:11,802
Hey, my friend. We meet again!

250
00:15:14,241 --> 00:15:15,361
Well, we're not friends.

251
00:15:16,121 --> 00:15:17,521
You look down on our school.

252
00:15:18,162 --> 00:15:19,442
Why would I be friends with you?

253
00:15:20,361 --> 00:15:21,401
Juan is right.

254
00:15:22,121 --> 00:15:24,282
Why is an outsider wandering around our school?

255
00:15:24,842 --> 00:15:25,862
What a show-off.

256
00:15:25,862 --> 00:15:27,322
And why are you wearing our uniform?

257
00:15:29,562 --> 00:15:30,902
Wait, isn't that my uniform?

258
00:15:30,902 --> 00:15:33,322
Uh, I took it. He needs it for a while.

259
00:15:33,322 --> 00:15:34,601
I'll give it back to you after he leaves.

260
00:15:38,496 --> 00:15:40,641
