261
00:15:42,368 --> 00:15:43,802
Oh, I remember now.

262
00:15:43,802 --> 00:15:45,301
I've seen your photo.

263
00:15:45,301 --> 00:15:47,061
Aren't you Lu Yao from Puhua High School?

264
00:15:47,061 --> 00:15:48,701
Could you keep it down?

265
00:15:48,701 --> 00:15:50,922
