and side with the enemy?

268
00:15:55,441 --> 00:15:56,721
Whose side are you on?

269
00:15:59,121 --> 00:16:01,202
I asked Lin Yujing to get me this uniform.

270
00:16:01,202 --> 00:16:03,520
She didn't help me on purpose. Don't blame her.

271
00:16:03,520 --> 00:16:06,222
If what I just said is a bit too much,

272
00:16:06,222 --> 00:16:07,421
I apologize.

273
00:16:07,421 --> 00:16:09,262
After all, friendship comes first.

274
00:16:09,262 --> 00:16:11,282
If you feel offended,

275
00:16:11,802 --> 00:16:14,362
