279
00:16:21,322 --> 00:16:23,241
Our Liying Middle School has more talents.

280
00:16:23,842 --> 00:16:24,962
When the sport meet officially begins,

281
00:16:24,962 --> 00:16:26,062
Juan will…

282
00:16:26,062 --> 00:16:27,264
Juan?

283
00:16:29,001 --> 00:16:31,401
If you're done with your business,
hurry up and leave.

284
00:16:32,682 --> 00:16:33,922
The next time you come,

285
00:16:33,922 --> 00:16:35,802
don't casually judge your friend's school.

286
00:16:38,962 --> 00:16:40,736
And don't make reckless decisions for her.

287
00:16:45,440 --> 00:16:46,592
Alright.

288
00:16:46,592 --> 00:16:50,821
Since you think what I said earlier was unfair,

289
00:16:50,821 --> 00:16:52,402
